> Hi all,
>
> Thanks for your help (Whit especially) on various things. After a fair bit
> of effort I got rccpbugs installed on my Mac 10.7 in R.app. ?Here's my
> setup:
>
>> sessionInfo()
> R version 2.14.1 (2011-12-22)
